001186  1               
001186  1                  ; --- HIT ---
001186  1  74 rr           stz ibul_active,x         ; deactivate this bullet
001188  1  20 5A 10        jsr update_inv_bullet_sprite
00118B  1  20 94 11        jsr player_hit
