0013F3  1               ;******************************************************************
0013F3  1               ; next_wave — advance wave counter, reduce speed, reset grid, resume play
0013F3  1               ;   Keeps: player X, lives, score, shields.
0013F3  1               ;   Clears: bullets, invaders, explosion, UFO.
